{"tid":1470244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［高手請入］在情在理，唔需要道歉，只需要國際級文宣洗白","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T11:38:32.000Z","uid":300554,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"227418088b8cde15d8a0370ca3189eef976c6367","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"唔認同機場捉鬼，但會發生係<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>在情在理</strong></span><br />\n所以無需要就此事對外<del>道歉</del>；<br />\n要做嘅係對內<strong>檢討</strong>：<br />\n機場發生捉鬼會令輿論失據，所以要避免<br />\n同埋對外文宣<strong>洗白</strong>：<br />\n以後嘅和理飛，要調整<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>文宣方向</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一，唯一道歉點係，sorry for inconvenience caused，而且要<span style=\"color: blue;\">令人明白個cause來自政府</span>；<br />\n<br />\n二，<span style=\"color: green;\">攤開警暴證據</span>俾遊客自己睇就夠，喱兩日機場集中仇警係可以理解的，但仇恨氣氛太大無可能達到和理非，令遊客同情了但法國都有警暴喔；<br />\n<br />\n三，同情了又如何？就要向旅客彰顯<span style=\"color: orange;\">香港國際地位</span>，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港人道同法治認知</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港為全球把關對抗邪惡共狗，共狗係全球共敵</span>⋯喚起同理心令旅客覺得<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>香港民族</strong></span>值得珍重，驅使國際社會利用香港喱隻棋打共，達至世界性和理<br />\n<br />\n印象中只有頭兩三次和理飛有出現過類似嘅資訊性文宣：由no extradition bill帶到國際性地位，後來就被仇警文宣淹沒了。喱個講到國際時政咁複雜，唔係一兩句tagline咁簡單，係要經準確分析嘅資料性文宣，所以請高手出手。<br />\n<br />\n我淨係知國際形勢好撚緊張！咁代表咩啊？有危有機啊！精明嘅香港人啲投機精神去咗邊？我哋要絕處逢生，要刀仔鋸大樹，要做世界級公民，要喺國際社會做世界！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721aba4444f0ef928da83c88da41146ed1c555cb","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"喱個係小弟喱兩晚嘅參與，觀察、理解、同埋檢討。"},{"pid":"ce1fde172c895d186ae2cfa5c69eb189b45ab144","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"在情在理，不割席不篤灰不分化，只需要檢討🛀🏻"},{"pid":"9cc1bc24b0cc54256ab7544d3ccff1d27eb8c770","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"就算唔係落手做文宣，去得機場都要幫手宣傳。"},{"pid":"1c829c74c9c69269da34103c7d80d98ecc654c37","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:41:01.000Z","msg":"我哋每一個都係親善大使，係公關，係外交官！"},{"pid":"0e9f90eff7fa883243c0f6cf7f04b98362e31951","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:41:40.000Z","msg":"無咩事，小弟出返去練下啲英文"},{"pid":"c1189640e379a795d927c8e912660c2d3149d9d0","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"等你哋啲高汁文宣啊！"},{"pid":"3a8bf342f46ffee90333a4e1fdb85597a4586f1d","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"唔洗好高深，就講香港人點樣be water，喱個東方荷里活曾經有個李小龍，前人留低嘅哲理，我哋後人識得咁樣應用！"},{"pid":"32172ada10611b685cf0d5c353d8e0fb04405bdb","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"推到攬炒團隊見到"},{"pid":"ce19577ec03876390cd0fcf45c4b0c38863262c0","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"推到攬炒入埋機場"},{"pid":"d35d64fc13fc419f054a36388cf5ccc64ab145d4","tid":1470244,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:58:00.000Z","msg":"聽日要派糖 但絕對唔可以道歉!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aecQeeU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aecQeeU</a>"},{"pid":"92eae1c8b8f7fdef0fbbfd1a2db5b0d9a50df143","tid":1470244,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa676ee1dfc90c9d9b0fc38c9b4807ff62512e81","tid":1470244,"uid":280020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"227418088b8cde15d8a0370ca3189eef976c6367","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"唔認