dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75ce3477f29241c667bb1f4d5f9945a12bf05bc1","tid":1470244,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"同意唔道歉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"不需要為捉鬼道歉<br />\n但對於旅客遇到的不便，我哋出手相助，要求航空公司提供清晰資訊，安撫旅客喺機場逗留嘅時間，最緊要話到俾旅客知我哋同一陣線，喱個世界合力推倒獨裁暴政"},{"pid":"47c168449b88ee0b07f07fde410147569dacc400","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02c3fa5486e7c397773137c62ec3bca10719ece8","tid":1470244,"uid":263557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1m8x5t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1m8x5t.png&h=24d07e0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"延伸討論 LiberateHongKong 講香港人願景<br />\n由政制、經濟、民生到文化等等去講<br />\n俾人睇到香港人係有理想<br />\n喱種理想有利於全球進步"},{"pid":"ea1e83e6ab1ce25eff29b52c7546795d6a743f30","tid":1470244,"uid":127489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:35:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5851c544bf70e94b26c1ae5c162e810c50c3bc08","tid":1470244,"uid":296341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:38:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21a86f7b97d82119f2d0a038864b47bcb784a1b2","tid":1470244,"uid":290211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"集思廣益，入黎討論下開多條戰線啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[機場拆局] 對準政權 輿論Spin返去醫護集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0c508bca512cff512b6058c3142b4b6892bba15","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5851c544bf70e94b26c1ae5c162e810c50c3bc08","tid":1470244,"uid":296341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:38:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:08:58.000Z","msg":"全世界一條船<br />\nTogether fight against the evil force"},{"pid":"d2c426154343b56d2e37e73daac5adaa2c2d4578","tid":1470244,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:24:52.000Z","msg":"完全認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07582ecbd14f54a192a453b85b1cf5df96e46cd3","tid":1470244,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"227418088b8cde15d8a0370ca3189eef976c6367","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"唔認同機場捉鬼，但會發生係<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>在情在理</strong></span><br />\n所以無需要就此事對外<del>道歉</del>；<br />\n要做嘅係對內<strong>檢討</strong>：<br />\n機場發生捉鬼會令輿論失據，所以要避免<br />\n同埋對外文宣<strong>洗白</strong>：<br />\n以後嘅和理飛，要調整<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>文宣方向</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一，唯一道歉點係，sorry for inconvenience caused，而且要<span style=\"color: blue;\">令人明白個cause來自政府</span>；<br />\n<br />\n二，<span style=\"color: green;\">攤開警暴證據</span>俾遊客自己睇就夠，喱兩日機場集中仇警係可以理解的，但仇恨氣氛太大無可能達到和理非，令遊客同情了但法國都有警暴喔；<br />\n<br />\n三，同情了又如何？就要向旅客彰顯<span style=\"color: orange;\">香港國際地位</span>，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港人道同法治認知</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港為全球把關對抗邪惡共狗，共狗係全球共敵</span>⋯喚起同理心令旅客覺得<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>香港民族</strong></span>值得珍重，驅使國際社會利用香港喱隻棋打共，達至世界性和理<br />\n<br />\n印象中只有頭兩三次和理飛有出現過類似嘅資訊性文宣：由no extradition bill帶到國際性地位，後來就被仇警文宣淹沒了。喱個講到國際時政咁複雜，唔係一兩句tagline咁簡單，係要經準確分析嘅資料性文宣，所以請高手出手。<br />\n<br />\n我淨係知國際形勢好撚緊張！咁代表咩啊？有危有機啊！精明嘅香港人啲投機精神去咗邊？我哋要絕處逢生，要刀仔鋸大樹，要做世界級公民，要喺國際社會做世界！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:49:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"909f2081be1655c8a03fd20a2a1aa64705fc8edd","tid":1470244,"uid":296341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:11:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"817d05b066dfd39ed30e3903cbe7e62fd558328b","tid":1470244,