8e7d8c5619d2b9d8e4adfdf872","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人之所以到今時今日都仲寸得起<br />\n因為香港人講廣東話大<br />\n香港人嘅母語思維 係有種抵死無喱頭<br />\n係時候將喱種幽默感轉化成英文<br />\n同外國人開心share <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c18495cbc5d3d873c91804139212bc67728b40c","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:17:07.000Z","msg":"「英美港盟，主權在民」<br />\n8.16 8點 遮打花園"},{"pid":"7685e0ea1bb7c12226cce0912c2aaf20befdfe72","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3TnF6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3TnF6E.jpg&h=0fc00285&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a32c4691ed58ec95325a93d5a4fc2b3151c3b9d5","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9RwHF6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9RwHF6N.jpg&h=f72903a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58ed845820ad9235b81d1f9519ee7a0470bb9ade","tid":1470244,"uid":195827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"國際文宣仲要要求外國公民對佢地嘅政府施壓<br />\n<br />\n做出不利港共嘅政策 好似禁催淚彈出口 香港關係法 人道救援/監察 聯合國提案(雖然中國有絕對否決權)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你想由處理輿論入手 可以去道歉/做文宣/解釋背景由來<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解我地會咁做</span></span> 同埋政府點樣反擊我地<br />\n<br />\n 動之以情 話我們幾個月黎承受嘅壓迫係非一般人能想像 再比人挑釁做間諜好容易失控 <br />\n不過我地已經係使用左非致命非永久傷害 並非不可原諒<br />\n<br />\n說之以理 拎popo 公安扮示威者嘅證據出黎 話極有可能係佢地自己嘅苦肉計 自己人打自己人 亦有警察煽動示威者打人/警察打人 從而令警察同政府得利"},{"pid":"0733c2edae50c9836b8634481573ee3a9fa67f04","tid":1470244,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲：食咗好多粒特效藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}